              Popular Diagnostic Centre is one of the leading healthcare
              providers in Bangladesh, offering advanced medical diagnostics,
              specialized treatments, and quality hospital services. With modern
              technology and expert doctors, it is trusted by millions of
              patients nationwide.
            </p>
            <a
